					<h3>Harness your professional world.</h3>
					<p>We're somehow "connected" to thousands of people, but how might we get to know friends of our friends? SixDegree is a conceptual tool that helps job seekers and recruiters alike to gain context and insight into one's aggregated networks.
					</p>
				</div>
