					<p>
						Networking is a two-sided coin, and our interviews revealed that recruiters have similar problems for slightly different reasons. Recruiters currently suffer low yield, scattering their time across various sources. Follow-up and follow-through are the most difficult components of recruiting, so SixDegree aimed to improve on  recruiter-candidate communication channels. 
